reviewText: Awesome set all the a I like in one combo can't go wrong with that. It for here fast in all in one piece.
Product was exactly what I wanted. Arrived on time and I would purchase from this vendor again. I would recommend others purchase from here as well.

This was a gift to my daughter as I have seen these movies before. My daughter and I rate the 4 movie DVD as very good. It should be noted that the movie Carlito's Way is NOT the version with Al Pacino.
I bought this to get the Mobsters dvd but found that the others movies were good also.  Getting 4 movies for the price of one is really a good deal.
This DVD is packed with 4 great movies including Jersey drive. Great deal for the price and the picture quality is great. Fast shipping. A+++ rating.
Accurate descrpition and shipped on time

Although I don't regret purchasing this, I probably won't watch it again until the middle of the next boring Winter.
New Jersey Drive is good (not great) but it's too d*** long! It could have cut out 30 minutes and easily made it's point.
Empire is another narrated, unoriginal, copy-cat movie. Okay to watch if you're snowed in.
Mobsters is one star! A Godfather rip-off! |Characters have absolutely no depth. Shallow and unconvincing. Anthony Quinn makes a buffoon of himself. You would never know he was a much better actor. A waste of their money and my time.
Carlito's way, Rise to Power had a good plot. Surprise and interesting ending. In my opinion, this was the best of the bunch.
Seann Combs seemed to turn in to a better actor as the movie moved along.
Sometimes movies get better, some times they get worse after you watch them a second time.
I won't know until next winter.
BOUGHT THIS FOR THE MOBSTERS MOVIE, BUT 2 OTHERS WERE GOOD ALSO.

New Jersey Drive, Empire and Carlitos Way Rise To Power are all great movies! I've never seen the Mobsters movie but I'll give it a shot once my dvd arrives. This is a great buy considering I bought it used for less than $5 with shipping.

Nothing better than to get 4 classic movies on one dvd at a great price!  I was only looking for one of these movies at the time but ended up not being able to pass up on this deal for all 4 classic movies.  This DVD is excellent for those extended movie nights with family members or sleepovers with friends who want the movie night to continue into the later night hours.  It would be great to find more selection combos such as this one!
